

@host = http://localhost:3002
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### API Root
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Health Check
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{host}}/health

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Blockchain
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/chain

### Validate Blockchain
GET {{baseUrl}}/chain/valid

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Transactions
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions

### Pending Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/pending

### Create Transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAddress": "alice",
  "toAddress": "charlie",
  "amount": 25
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Mining
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/mine
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "minerAddress": "miner-1"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Balance
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
@USER1=address1
GET {{baseUrl}}/balance/{{USER1}}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Statistics
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Wallets
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Create Wallet
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets

### Wallet Details
@USER2=address2
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/{{USER2}}